00:37:44.140 --> 00:37:45.640 align:middle line:84%
So we are spiritual
beings having

00:37:45.640 --> 00:37:47.660 align:middle line:90%
a human experience in a body.

00:37:47.660 --> 00:37:50.740 align:middle line:84%
But our consciousness
expands outside the body,

00:37:50.740 --> 00:37:52.320 align:middle line:90%
but it goes through it, right?

00:37:52.320 --> 00:37:56.060 align:middle line:84%
So what happens to
