00:37:56.060 --> 00:38:00.790 align:middle line:84%
the prefrontal cortex or the
part of the brain that's smart

00:38:00.790 --> 00:38:04.830 align:middle line:84%
goes silent, because the
amygdala or the ancient brain

00:38:04.830 --> 00:38:09.940 align:middle line:84%
gets awoken because it's
signaled that it's not safe.

00:38:09.940 --> 00:38:11.940 align:middle line:84%
So your ability
to make decisions

00:38:11.940 --> 00:38:16.710 align:middle line:84%
in the enmeshed moments are
actually taken away from you.

00:38:16.710 --> 00:38:22.270 align:middle line:84%
Because what's happening
is that your neuropeptides,

00:38:22.270 --> 00:38:25.130 align:middle line:84%
the molecules of
emotion, then will

00:38:25.130 --> 00:38:27.100 align:middle line:84%
go and speak to the
receptor cells that

00:38:27.100 --> 00:38:28.580 align:middle line:90%
will release hormones.

00:38:28.580 --> 00:38:30.760 align:middle line:84%
If you're happy,
you'll get dopamine.

00:38:30.760 --> 00:38:32.750 align:middle line:84%
If you're stressed,
which most of us are,

00:38:32.750 --> 00:38:34.490 align:middle line:84%
you're going to
get the adrenalin.

00:38:34.490 --> 00:38:37.810 align:middle line:84%
Now in the old days,
