So we would run really fast.

00:38:42.140 --> 00:38:43.270 align:middle line:90%
Fantastic.

00:38:43.270 --> 00:38:45.750 align:middle line:84%
And then the stress would
go through our bodies.

00:38:45.750 --> 00:38:48.430 align:middle line:84%
And we would need
a lot of glucose

00:38:48.430 --> 00:38:51.180 align:middle line:84%
because we ask for
glucose, right?

00:38:51.180 --> 00:38:52.100 align:middle line:90%
So we want to run.

00:38:52.100 --> 00:38:54.890 align:middle line:84%
And then what happens is
if we're stuck in a cave,

00:38:54.890 --> 00:38:56.420 align:middle line:90%
we're in there.

00:38:56.420 --> 00:38:57.990 align:middle line:84%
We might be in
