with Hay House.

00:40:43.790 --> 00:40:45.206 align:middle line:84%
Because I thought
I had it licked.

00:40:45.206 --> 00:40:45.860 align:middle line:90%
I got there.

00:40:45.860 --> 00:40:49.460 align:middle line:84%
While I was looking,
while I was watching,

00:40:49.460 --> 00:40:50.830 align:middle line:90%
I was a vegan vegetarian.

00:40:50.830 --> 00:40:53.037 align:middle line:84%
I was being super
clean with my eating.

00:40:53.037 --> 00:40:55.120 align:middle line:84%
And I was making sure I
was eating enough protein.

00:40:55.120 --> 00:40:57.110 align:middle line:84%
That's why I
watched my food so I

00:40:57.110 --> 00:40:59.440 align:middle line:84%
know I wasn't doing
anything wrong.

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:02.000 align:middle line:84%
I still put on 25 pounds
while I went on tour

00:41:02.000 --> 00:41:04.480 align:middle line:84%
with Sylvia Browne as her
opening speaker at Hay House.

00:41:04.480 --> 00:41:07.410 align:middle line:84%
Terrified of the audience,
terrified of the experience.

00:41:07.410 --> 00:41:09.660 align:middle line:84%
Having all these people that
needed something from me,

00:41:09.660 --> 00:41:11.630 align:middle line:84%
not knowing where I
ended and they began.

00:41:11.630 --> 00:41:13.570 align:middle line:90%
And I just started swelling.

00:41:13.570 --> 00:41:15.589 align:middle line:84%
So that's when it
was like, oh, my god.

00:41:15.589 --> 00:41:18.130 align:middle line:84%
I've got to be, like, a forensic
CSI agent now and figure out

00:41:18.130 --> 00:41:18.914 align:middle line:90%
what this is.

00:41:18.914 --> 00:41:20.580 align:middle line:84%
And I noticed how
many overweight people

00:41:20.580 --> 00:41:23.450 align:middle line:84%
were in the audience,
and their stories.

00:41:23.450 --> 00:41:25.520 align:middle line:90%
And over the years, wow.

00:41:25.520 --> 00:41:26.040 align:middle line:90%
Jeez.

00:41:26.040 --> 00:41:28.430 align:middle line:84%
Empathy equals-- people
who feel too much

00:41:28.430 --> 00:41:30.630 align:middle line:84%
equals having
problems with weight.

